dct_title_s: A historical and classical atlas, illustrating, by a series of maps and charts, ancient history and geography, both sacred and profane; and, Grecian and Roman mythology. With two additional charts, illustrating civil and ecclesiastical history, from the birth of Christ to the present time.
dct_alternative_sm: A historical and classical atlas, illustrating, by a series of maps and charts, ancient history and geography, both sacred and profane; and, Grecian and Roman mythology. With two additional charts, illustrating civil and ecclesiastical history, from the birth of Christ to the present time.
dct_description_sm: 2 unnumbered pages : 3 maps (1 double), 9 illustrations (5 double) ; 43 cm.
